additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children and pets. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Wear suitable gloves. People suffering from perfume sensitivity should be cautious when using this product. Air fresheners do not replace good hygiene practices. Notice: Product contains parts that may pose a choking hazard. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26: New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor.
